<div class="res-text richtextContent background-opaque" id="25504194-0071-4d27-a82b-97edaeaa69ad" >

    <p>Welcome to your movement break! This is your chance to recharge your mind and body during those quick moments in between classes, meetings, study sessions, or whatever life throws your way.</p> 
<p>Choose your break time below to find an activity that works for you! Activities are updated multiple times per week, so check back often.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#25504194-0071-4d27-a82b-97edaeaa69ad");});</script></div>

				

				
