		<div class="iconContainer"><span aria-hidden='true' class='icon fa fa-map'></span></div>
		<div class="textContainer"><p>Special thanks to our friends from&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/thriveru/tia/">Thriving in Action</a>, <a href="https://www.facebook.com/rumoodroutes/">Mood Routes<span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a> and <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/studentaffairs/storytelling/">Student Affairs Storytelling</a>&nbsp;for their inspiration and partnership on physical activity as a learning strategy and 'emoji card' assessments.</p></div>
	</div>
